类 Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet.Vector

  • public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
    Rolls, pitches, and yaws a three-dimensional vector. This tiny vector class is optimized for rolling, pitching, and yawing of a three-vector.

    Peli
